Welcome to Fisher & Douglas, LLP

 
 
 
 




Our firm was founded in 1989 by partners Mark Fisher and David Douglas with a simple philosophy. We see ourselves as problem-solvers. Our goal is to use our knowledge and experience to solve our clients’ problems.
Fisher & Douglas’s services include Business and Corporate Law, Real Estate Law, Probate and Estate Law and more!
Is there a problem we can solve for you? Please Contact Us to arrange for a consultation. We look forward to hearing from you.

 

