Product Description▼▲
The practice of praying at the beginning and end of every day has been used by people in many religious traditions. It is a way to sanctify the passing of the hours, placing our work and our lives in God's hands. No matter how busy your day, Morning Prayer, Evening Praise offers a structure to transform your time into God's.

