Publisher's Description▼▲
"Morning Prayer, Evening Praise" includes classic prayers from a wide variety of writers, such as Augustine, Julian, Bonhoeffer, Native Americans, and sources from around the world. The book includes 30 each of morning and evening prayers directed to God. Each includes an invitation to pray, Scripture, prayer, and a closing.


